## Conversation History
user: 
请为以下MCP工具生成测试用例:

工具名称: Fetcher MCP
作者: jae-jae
描述: 用于通过 Playwright 无头浏览器获取网页内容的 MCP 服务器。支持智能内容提取和多样的输出格式。需要通过 'npx playwright install chromium' 安装 Playwright 浏览器。
类别: 实用工具
包名: fetcher-mcp
API密钥需求: 否
API密钥列表: 无

可用工具列表:
[
  {
    "name": "fetch_url",
    "description": "Retrieve web page content from a specified URL",
    "inputSchema": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "url": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "URL to fetch"
        },
        "timeout": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Page loading timeout in milliseconds, default is 30000 (30 seconds)"
        },
        "waitUntil": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Specifies when navigation is considered complete, options: 'load', 'domcontentloaded', 'networkidle', 'commit', default is 'load'"
        },
        "extractContent": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to intelligently extract the main content, default is true"
        },
        "maxLength": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Maximum length of returned content (in characters), default is no limit"
        },
        "returnHtml": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to return HTML content instead of Markdown, default is false"
        },
        "waitForNavigation": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to wait for additional navigation after initial page load (useful for sites with anti-bot verification), default is false"
        },
        "navigationTimeout": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Maximum time to wait for additional navigation in milliseconds, default is 10000 (10 seconds)"
        },
        "disableMedia": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to disable media resources (images, stylesheets, fonts, media), default is true"
        },
        "debug": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to enable debug mode (showing browser window), overrides the --debug command line flag if specified"
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "url"
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "fetch_urls",
    "description": "Retrieve web page content from multiple specified URLs",
    "inputSchema": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "urls": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "description": "Array of URLs to fetch"
        },
        "timeout": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Page loading timeout in milliseconds, default is 30000 (30 seconds)"
        },
        "waitUntil": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Specifies when navigation is considered complete, options: 'load', 'domcontentloaded', 'networkidle', 'commit', default is 'load'"
        },
        "extractContent": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to intelligently extract the main content, default is true"
        },
        "maxLength": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Maximum length of returned content (in characters), default is no limit"
        },
        "returnHtml": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to return HTML content instead of Markdown, default is false"
        },
        "waitForNavigation": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to wait for additional navigation after initial page load (useful for sites with anti-bot verification), default is false"
        },
        "navigationTimeout": {
          "type": "number",
          "description": "Maximum time to wait for additional navigation in milliseconds, default is 10000 (10 seconds)"
        },
        "disableMedia": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to disable media resources (images, stylesheets, fonts, media), default is true"
        },
        "debug": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether to enable debug mode (showing browser window), overrides the --debug command line flag if specified"
        }
      },
      "required": [
        "urls"
      ]
    }
  }
]

请生成3-5个最重要的测试用例来验证这个MCP工具的核心功能（严格不要超过5个）。优先选择最具代表性的测试场景。

message.content:
```json
{
  "test_cases": [
    {
      "name": "基础连通性测试",
      "description": "验证工具是否可以成功启动并响应基本请求。",
      "tool_name": "fetch_url",
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://example.com"
      },
      "expected_type": "success",
      "expected_result": "成功返回网页内容",
      "priority": "high"
    },
    {
      "name": "单个URL获取测试",
      "description": "测试工具是否能正确通过 fetch_url 获取指定URL的网页内容。",
      "tool_name": "fetch_url",
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://example.com",
        "timeout": 30000,
        "waitUntil": "load",
        "extractContent": true
      },
      "expected_type": "success",
      "expected_result": "返回指定网页的提取内容",
      "priority": "high"
    },
    {
      "name": "多个URL获取测试",
      "description": "测试工具是否能正确通过 fetch_urls 同时处理多个URL并返回对应内容。",
      "tool_name": "fetch_urls",
      "parameters": {
        "urls": ["https://example.com", "https://example.org"],
        "timeout": 30000,
        "extractContent": true
      },
      "expected_type": "success",
      "expected_result": "返回两个网页的提取内容",
      "priority": "high"
    },
    {
      "name": "错误处理测试 - 无效URL",
      "description": "测试工具在提供无效URL时是否能正确处理错误并返回提示。",
      "tool_name": "fetch_url",
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://invalid-url-that-does-not-exist.com",
        "timeout": 10000
      },
      "expected_type": "error",
      "expected_result": "返回超时或连接失败错误",
      "priority": "normal"
    },
    {
      "name": "参数验证测试 - 超长内容限制",
      "description": "测试工具是否能正确应用 maxLength 参数限制返回内容长度。",
      "tool_name": "fetch_url",
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://example.com",
        "maxLength": 100
      },
      "expected_type": "success",
      "expected_result": "返回的内容长度不超过100个字符",
      "priority": "normal"
    }
  ]
}
```
